      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab><supplied reason="explanation">This is the</supplied> tomb of <seg cert="low">Jordanes</seg> from the stem of
Eulalios, whom chilly virgin justice had as a worthy servant; but
jealous, hatefully-named Fate snatched him quickly, <supplied cert="low" reason="explanation">he who was</supplied>
splendid <gap reason="lost"/> <seg cert="low">taking away</seg>.</ab>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="IX.21">IX.21</xref>.</p>
      </div>

